The '''1909 [[VMI Keydets]] football team''' represented the [[Virginia Military Institute]] in their nineteenth ever season of organized football. First-year coach [[William Gloth]] lead VMI to a 4-3 season.<ref name="VMI">http://www.vmikeydets.com/pdf8/708636.pdf</ref>
